Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:06.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.51,0:00:09.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:44.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,礙事！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你和它有關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:22.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是在問你和「夜禍」有沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:24.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道的話就不要再扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:03.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:08.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣你就應該知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,它不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是夜晚的禍害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:29.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:38.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,繭子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:46.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,吵得這麼厲害 無論是誰都會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:48.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:49.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:52.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是個小鬼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還是叫一下救護車什麼的比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:04.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:24.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,它是夜晚的禍害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:57.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這雲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫什麼雲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:02.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 積雨雲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:03.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天的雲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好像天空中有座山一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,它甚至被稱為雲峰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一般的綿雲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是你救了我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說不上是救…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不還禮的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:31.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還禮？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:47.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:48.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還想要我做些什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,想要你做些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能做到的話 什麼都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:57.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,應該有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:06.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,色狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:07.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:10.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我為你做飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:13.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我什麼都還沒說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又得重來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.64,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,森宮 森宮依人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.42,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 請假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.01,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,森宮經常請假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,從昨天開始就讓人覺得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:43.96,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都已經是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:45.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很讓人擔心呢  真名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.63,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,自己要好好注意身體喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個只懂得天空的傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:53.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有句「傻瓜不會感冒」的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:56.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又是和天空有關的事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 總覺得有點不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不接 沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:15.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因為有更擔心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:23.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再有一會兒就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 把這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:28.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有點小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:37.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好 三分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:40.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:00.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要突然過來阻止嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛不是要踢了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:03.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不是自動販賣機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:09.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:13.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,機器的話 用踢的就什麼毛病都可以修好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這還是第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:17.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:22.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:28.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:30.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:32.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕只有微波爐得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但原本是要致謝的… 飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:37.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,致謝的話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:39.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為已經摸過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 來聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:47.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:48.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 突然之間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你看起來沒有朋友 挺寂寞的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就重新來自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宮依人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,15歲 高一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,家人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有一個姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:12.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要光讓我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:19.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:21.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,被你看到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,即使我想保密也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:44.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:14.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我… 不是人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宮小姐怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好吃藥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能進行正確的檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:37.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,知道的對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有必要？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:44.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊有病人正在叫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:51.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:10.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 有點多管閒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:20.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:22.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:33.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:35.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是姊姊才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:39.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 小依總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:39.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也不來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:52.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在經濟產業省主辦的ECO-Bag競賽中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:52.27,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,[ECO-Bag]:Ecology bag（無環境污染提袋）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:56.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,入選作品也是使用由該項技術得以再生的再生布
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夜禍人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不老不死的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以從很早以前就總是被追殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天黑後我就會出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我並沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:22.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不能見陽光的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:30.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:31.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:33.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很厲害吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,活了好幾百年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:39.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,卻一次都沒有在真正的藍天下站立過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:45.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那光亮 那穿透廣闊無邊的空間的藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:48.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:52.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:56.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你說在拍藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 連累你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:03.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是晚間新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:10.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:15.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯… 怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:16.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男的沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會再來？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:24.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,總會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,反正直到現在都還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為無論怎麼受傷 也不會輕易死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:35.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:36.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:57.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:01.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了 待在這裡比較安全
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,待在這裡的話 不用擔心被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:06.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不會和誰說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:07.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,父母也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:09.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說了沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:13.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說了嗎 這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:16.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和那沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:22.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為和我在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你總有一天會變得憎恨我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:32.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:40.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:41.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是真名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:46.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:48.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃說要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:51.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說是因為依人不來所以就要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 馬上就去！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:57.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:01.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:04.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:07.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就回來 等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:10.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有話想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一時半會兒的沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:13.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:18.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:33.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:54.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:01.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:02.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:12.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:24.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:25.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 繭子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:31.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的名菜應該是海鮮才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:35.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是我決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:47.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還是好好地跟我說一下發生了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說過好幾次了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:51.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:53.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夜禍沒在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:55.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:56.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:11.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:15.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也沒來醫院 又沒接電話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:20.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,並不想要那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,電燈關著的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:32.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:35.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:55.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼隨便就進來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,本來並不打算進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:50.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好狡猾啊… 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:54.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空就是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不 比這更美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:16.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,更加更加地寬廣 美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:42.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天會給你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:45.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:33.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,sola小知識
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:33.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:35.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,豆科1年 2年生植物中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:38.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有豌豆 蠶豆也稱天豆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:40.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,它們原產於西南亞洲或北非
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:44.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,據說傳到日本是在8世紀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:23.20,FBT,NTP,0,0,360,,{\fad(1000,1000)}仰望蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:45.65,FBT,NTP,640,0,224,,平穩的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:01:01.89,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}羽根が白く光り 眩しく飛んで行く
